STORY 11.5 - HIT A SIXER GAMIFICATION
SYSTEM
Complete Technical Specification & Implementation Guide
Sprint: 12
Story Points: 13
Priority: High
Type: Feature - Gamification
Dependencies: User authentication, Subscription system (Story 11.1), Payment integration
EPIC CONTEXT
Build a cricket-themed daily gamification system ("Hit a Sixer") that:
-
-
-
-
-
-
Is available ONLY to paid subscribers (₹99/month platform fee)
Awards wallet credits based on probability (8% FOUR=₹50, 4% SIXER=₹100, 88%
OUT=₹10)
Allows one play per user per day (resets midnight IST)
Must be played before 6:00 PM IST
Credits expire 30 days after earning
Credits auto-apply at session booking checkout
USER STORY
As a MANAS360 subscriber
I want to play a daily cricket game to win wallet credits
So that I can reduce my therapy session costs and feel rewarded for being a subscriber
